text: oka pravaktanu kuda! Atanu miku spastamaina allah sucanalanu (ayat lanu) vinipistunnadu. Adi, visvasinci satkaryalu cesevarini andhakarala nundi veluguloniki tisukuravataniki. Mariyu allah nu visvasinci satkaryalu cesevarini, ayana krinda selayellu pravahince svargavanalalo pravesimpajestadu. Akkada varu sasvatanga kalakalam untaru. Vastavaniki allah alanti vyakti koraku uttama jivanopadhini prasadincadu
